title: Jane Eyre
description: Read the first-person narrative of Jane Eyre that revolutionized the art of fiction. Jane Eyre explores the thems of classicism, sexism, religion and proto-feminism and follows the experiences of Jane Eyre as she grows to adulthood and falls in love with Mr. Rochester.  This digital edition from Xist Classics features a beautifully formatted and professionally proofed version of the original text.
